						               													<description>ENGLISH&amp;#10;This game is set in the city of Barcelona, and it's based on the &amp;quot;Taxi Driver&amp;quot; comic by the illustrator and author Bi&amp;eacute;. It takes you into the world of the night shift of taxi drivers: your goal will be to take the highest number of passengers to their destinations. Learn languages to earn better tips from your customers, and improve your vehicle so you can carry more passengers. The driver who gets the highest revenues is the winner. Discover Barcelona in a different and thrilling way!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During his turn, a player can perform only ONE of the following actions. After that, his turn ends and the next player&amp;rsquo;s&amp;#10;turn starts. The possible actions are:&amp;#10;1. Look for Passengers (takes 2 passenger cards)&amp;#10;2. Improve language skills (place passenger card in a corner of driver card)&amp;#10;3. Take Passengers to a Destination (play cards of the hand to get a destination card)&amp;#10;4. Improve his vehicle (A player can improve his vehicle once&amp;#10;during the game by flipping his Driver card from side A to side B)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;ESPA&amp;Ntilde;OL&amp;#10;Ambientada en la ciudad de Barcelona, y basado en el c&amp;oacute;mic &amp;ldquo;Taxi Driver&amp;rdquo; del ilustrador e historietista Bi&amp;eacute;, convi&amp;eacute;rtete en un taxista del turno de noche con el objetivo de llevar al m&amp;aacute;ximo n&amp;uacute;mero de pasajeros a sus destinos, aprende idiomas para lograr mejores propinas y mejora tu veh&amp;iacute;culo para llevar m&amp;aacute;s clientes. El conductor que consiga la mayor recaudaci&amp;oacute;n ser&amp;aacute; el ganador del juego. Descubre la ciudad condal de una forma divertida y distinta.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;CATAL&amp;Agrave;&amp;#10;Ambientada a la ciutat de Barcelona, i basat en el c&amp;ograve;mic &amp;quot;Taxi Driver&amp;quot; de l'il &amp;bull; lustrador i historietista Bi&amp;eacute;, converteix-te en un taxista del torn de nit amb l'objectiu de portar al m&amp;agrave;xim nombre de passatgers als seus destins, apr&amp;egrave;n idiomes per aconseguir millors propines i millora el teu vehicle per portar m&amp;eacute;s clients. El conductor que aconsegueixi la major recaptaci&amp;oacute; ser&amp;agrave; el guanyador del joc. Descobreix la ciutat comtal d'una forma divertida i diferent.</description>
